overview.longBusinessSummary: Ryan Specialty Holdings, Inc. operates as a service provider of specialty products and solutions for insurance brokers, agents, and carriers in the United States, Canada, the United Kingdom, rest of Europe, India, and Singapore. The company offers distribution, underwriting, product development, administration, and risk management services by acting as a wholesale broker and a managing underwriter. It serves commercial, industrial, institutional, and government sectors. The company was founded in 2010 and is headquartered in Chicago, Illinois.
